{"type":"answer","id":16403,"parentType":"question","parentId":3340,"uid":3012,"contents":"&nbsp;其实有隐喻的太多了。下面说一个搞笑的，<br>\n周星驰在整蛊专家里的，周星驰吃了谎言豆沙包，<br>\n“我係古晶，六歲出嚟擦鞋幫補家計，八歲賣血幫阿媽醫病，十歲考會考攞九優一良，十五歲攞<a href=\"http://www.wikiwand.com/zh/%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%82%91%E5%87%BA%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">十大傑出青年</a>。我覺得自己好靚仔，<a href=\"http://www.wikiwand.com/zh/%E8%91%89%E5%AD%90%E6%A5%A3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">葉子楣</a>亦都好賢良淑德，<a href=\"http://www.wikiwand.com/zh/%E9%99%B3%E7%99%BE%E7%A5%A5\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">陳百祥</a>係世界上最叻嘅人，<a href=\"http://www.wikiwand.com/zh/%E8%A2%81%E6%9C%A8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">袁木</a>好誠實，<a href=\"http://www.wikiwand.com/zh/%E6%9D%8E%E9%B5%AC\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">李鵬</a>係我哋最偉大嘅領袖！”<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JyhO9DS.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JyhO9DS.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JyhO9DS.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-04-08","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}